<section class="create" id="create" aria-labelledby="create-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section-header">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">// 04 — Make your own</p>
      <h2 id="create-heading" class="section-title">Four steps to a published theme.</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">Each icon starts from a 128×128 SVG with a single placeholder <code>&lt;circle&gt;</code>. Restyle it, recolor it, give it depth — but keep the circle. The validator uses it to check fit and bounds.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="create-grid">
      <div>
        <ol class="create-steps">
          <li class="create-step">
            <h3>Download the template SVG</h3>
            <p>Start with <code>clarity-template.svg</code> — a 128×128 canvas with a centred placeholder circle on a transparent background. Use it once per icon.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="create-step">
            <h3>Open it in Inkscape <span class="pill pill--style">recommended</span></h3>
            <p>Any vector editor works (Affinity, Figma, Illustrator), but Inkscape preserves the <code>id</code> attribute on the placeholder circle, which the validator needs.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="create-step">
            <h3>Style the placeholder <span class="pill pill--required">don't delete</span></h3>
            <p>The circle with <code>id="icon-placeholder"</code> must remain in the file. You can change its <code>fill</code>, add a <code>filter</code>, apply a <code>mask</code>, wrap it in a <code>&lt;g&gt;</code>, or transform it. Add glyphs, gradients, and effects around it — just don't remove it.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="create-step">
            <h3>Upload &amp; submit</h3>
            <p>Drop the finished SVG into the validator. It runs the checks below and shows you a preview before it goes to the public gallery.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>

        <div class="create-snippet" aria-label="Template SVG source">
          <div class="create-snippet-head">
            <span>clarity-template.svg</span>
            <span>128 × 128 · transparent</span>
          </div>
<pre><span class="tok-comment">&lt;!-- The placeholder circle MUST stay. Style it any way you like. --&gt;</span>
<span class="tok-tag">&lt;svg</span> <span class="tok-attr">xmlns</span>=<span class="tok-str">"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"</span>
     <span class="tok-attr">viewBox</span>=<span class="tok-str">"0 0 128 128"</span> <span class="tok-attr">width</span>=<span class="tok-str">"128"</span> <span class="tok-attr">height</span>=<span class="tok-str">"128"</span><span class="tok-tag">&gt;</span>

  <span class="tok-tag">&lt;circle</span> <span class="tok-keep">id</span>=<span class="tok-str">"icon-placeholder"</span>
          <span class="tok-attr">cx</span>=<span class="tok-str">"64"</span> <span class="tok-attr">cy</span>=<span class="tok-str">"64"</span> <span class="tok-attr">r</span>=<span class="tok-str">"56"</span>
          <span class="tok-attr">fill</span>=<span class="tok-str">"#8b8d96"</span> <span class="tok-tag">/&gt;</span>

  <span class="tok-comment">&lt;!-- Your icon goes here. Glyphs, gradients, filters, --&gt;</span>
  <span class="tok-comment">&lt;!-- anything that fits inside the placeholder bounds. --&gt;</span>

<span class="tok-tag">&lt;/svg&gt;</span></pre>
        </div>

        <div class="create-actions">
          <a class="button button--primary" href="/upload">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-upload"/></svg>
            Upload your theme
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="template-card" aria-label="Template preview">
        <div class="template-preview">
          <svg class="template-svg" viewBox="0 0 128 128" role="img" aria-label="Template SVG: 128 by 128 canvas with centred placeholder circle">
            <line class="template-axis" x1="64" y1="0" x2="64" y2="128"/>
            <line class="template-axis" x1="0" y1="64" x2="128" y2="64"/>
            <rect class="template-bounds" x="1" y="1" width="126" height="126"/>
            <circle class="template-bounds" cx="64" cy="64" r="56"/>
            <circle class="template-placeholder" id="icon-placeholder" cx="64" cy="64" r="56"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="template-meta">
          <span>placeholder</span>
          <code>#icon-placeholder</code>
        </div>
        <div class="template-meta" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
          <span>canvas</span>
          <code>128 × 128</code>
        </div>
        <div class="template-actions">
          <a class="button button--ghost button--small" href="/template" download="clarity-template.svg">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-download"/></svg>
            Download SVG
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
